.env
__pycache__/
*/__pycache__/
.DS_Store
diagnose.py
counterra-positioning-and-roadmap.md

# Ignore everything under out/ EXCEPT the two artifacts the scheduled worker
# maintains: the running ledger itself, and the Base spend report as a public
# view of it. The CSV exports and per-chain variants are regenerable from the
# ledger in one command, and committing them caused constant local/bot
# collisions on every local run. Note we ignore out/* (contents), not out/
# (the dir), so these negations take effect.
out/*
!out/counterra.db
!out/spend_report_base.html
